Business models. Service design. Marketing. Business relations management. Personnel management. Strategic management. Financial management. Business internationalization. Risk assessment.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The aim of the course is to provide the knowledge and skills for analysing and developing the business model of an operating company.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  Upon the completion of the course the student: 1) is able to analyse the business model of an organization; 2) is able to implement principal methods and techniques of business analysis; 3) is able to analyse and improve functional areas of a business; 4) is able to implement design thinking for product/service development; 5) is able to design and develop organizational strategy.
